{
  "stem": "5613.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a whole group of all British subjects, only British civilians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we spent a day there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then in the evening, a bus came along and took us to Brussels, which is only half an hour away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they dropped us off in an exhibition hall, a very nice exhibition hall called the Cinquantenaire in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had banks, lovely banks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was, like, a balcony in front with big steps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We could sit there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But German guards were patrolling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were not allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we got food there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we thought, this is lovely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "To be a prisoner this way is a pleasure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we spent three days there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And on the fourth day, it was Friday morning, suddenly we hear shouting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But you know German shouting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] You know, I can't imitate them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was so rough and so like canon balls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was at 6:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we had to fall in-- in line, stand to attention, and we stood there from 6:00 in the morning till around 11:00, 11:30.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And all the time, there were three or four SS soldiers who were telling us they're going to shoot us, they're going to take us to Germany, and they're going to kill us, and they're going to bury us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You know, the worst that you-- and we believed them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we were standing for all these hours without moving.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Then around 11:30, a truck came along-- a German army truck-- or two, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they loaded us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were going east.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I know Belgium very well-- every village, every town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
